## Findings
- Video 1 (bO2W8jtyNTs):
    - Scene change frequency: High (every 2-4 seconds). Frequent use of AI-generated B-roll and tool screen recordings.
    - Subtitle style: Bold, phrase-based, bottom-centered. High visibility.
    - SFX/BGM: Upbeat, cinematic BGM. Whoosh SFX for transitions.
    - Visual elements: Screen recordings, AI imagery, text overlays for key points.
- Video 2 (n9ioRpwFLDI):
    - Scene change frequency: Moderate. Cuts between talking head and screen recordings/examples.
